'''Talal Selhami''' (yavutse ku ya 11 Werurwe 1982), ni  umukinnyi wa firime muri [[Maroke]] ukomoka mu [[bufaransa]] . <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/448787.html</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane ''Mirages'', ''Achoura'' hamwe ''nabashushanyaga Ibiremwa - The Frankenstein Complex'' . <ref name="sitges">https://sitgesfilmfestival.com/eng/fitxa_director?id=100301</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
yavutse ku ya 11 Werurwe 1982 i Neuilly-sur-Seine, Hauts-de-Seine mu Bufaransa nk'umuhererezi w'umuryango. Se, Mohamed Selhami ni umunyamakuru wa Maroc akaba ari nawe washinze ikinyamakuru Maroc Hebdo International. Yarangije icyiciro cya gatatu cya kaminuza mu buhanzi no kwidagadura, inzobere mu gukora, muri kaminuza ya Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne . <ref name="bifff">https://www.bifff.net/talal-selhami/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2005, yakoze umukobwa we muto ''Sinistra'' . <ref name="bifff" /> Nyuma yo gutsinda muri make, yakoze ''Partir en umwotsi'' muri 2007. Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana, ''Mirage'' . Iyi filime ihagarariwe kumugaragaro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Marrakech mu 2010 ndetse na Tangier National Film Festival muri 2011. Filime yaje gutsindira ibihembo bibiri: Kumashusho meza no Gusobanura neza Abagore. Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Bruxelles (BIFFF) i Buruseli, 2011 yakiriye filime idasanzwe y'abacamanza.

Ukuboza 2018, yasohoye filime ye ''Achoura, La nuit des enfants'' nk'umusaruro uhuriweho na Franco-Maroc. <ref>http://www.lesecransterribles.com/achoura-interview-talal-selhami/50159</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe mu minsi mikuru cumi n'itanu ku isi: harimo, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime mpuzamahanga rya Paris, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime ryiza ryabereye i Buruseli, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Bucheon (BiFan) muri Koreya y'Epfo ndetse na Neuchâtel International Fantastic Film Festival (NIFFF) muri Neuchâtel. Nyuma muri 2019, Talal yahawe igihembo cyumusaruro mwiza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Tangier ndetse n’abacamanza badasanzwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sitges .  Hagati aho, filime yanatanze igihembo cyiza cya Filime muri HARD: LINE International Film Festival mu [[Budage]]. 

